fr.sii.ogham.core.id.generator

Class SequentialIdGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.core.id.generator.SequentialIdGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdGenerator

    public class SequentialIdGenerator
extends Object
implements IdGenerator
    Generates a simple sequence:
    • Either 1, 2, 3, ..., n
    • Or <name>1, <name>2, <name>3, ..., <name>n

    Name is URL encoded

    If the generated id is greater than Long.MAX_VALUE, then it restarts from 0.
